name: v3.0.0
body:
### Thanks to all the contributors and users, OpenHub will be better because of you!

### New
* Add **Portuguese**(#121), **Korea**(#123), and **Spanish**(#198) translation
* Add **AMOLED**(#161) theme

### Improvements
* Better translations
* Make app move able to sd card(#154)

### Fixes
* Fix featured topics
* Fix WIKI inner link invalid(#196)
* Fix repository size overflow (#197)

name: v2.6.0
body:
### New
* Add german language support
* Display issue event and labels in issue detail page
* Support edit, add and delete your labels
* Support disable loading network image while mobile network, you can set it in settings ( #39 )

### Improvements
* Show warning dialog when close of reopen issue
* Add english and german date format ( #41 )
* Add all_languages and unknown_languages translation in strings ( #41 )

### Fixes
* Fix the crash of share in customtabs browser
* Fix chinese translation error of forked in news page ( #50 )
* Fix can't load more in search repositories page

name: v2.5.0
body:
### New
* Support all languages in trending, show total star num of today, this week, this month
* Improve the display of repositories language info, show languages color

### Fixes

name: v2.4.0
body:
### New
* Add featured topics
* Support mark all notifications as read ([#23](https://github.com/ThirtyDegreesRay/OpenHub/issues/23))
* Support custom tabs ([#22](https://github.com/ThirtyDegreesRay/OpenHub/issues/22))
* Display company info in profile page
* Support custom start page, adjust drawer item order

### Fixes
* Fix edit comment popup menu style in dark theme
* Fix wiki tile chinese garbled
* Fix crash when rotate screen

name: v2.3.0
body:
### New
* Add repository collections in drawer(Curated lists and insight into burgeoning industries, topics, and communities)

### Improvements
* Use release publish time instead of release created time when show release time
* Set copy clone url available in repository page
* Hide float action button when list scroll up
* Recover code position when screen rotation
* Add swipe to remove item tip in bookmarks
* Improve the display of markdown blockquote
* Improve the display of markdown image, add top and bottom margin

### Fixes
* Fix bug that links can't opend when don't contain http prefix
* Fix bug that list will crash in sometimes
* Fix bug that logout will crash after theme, language changed

name: v2.2.0
body:
### New
* New logo and new light teal theme

### Improvements
* Change tab layout selected color to title text color
* Improve chinese translation
* Fix that repos item show malformed when repos name too long
* Use break word to force wrap
* Add scrollbars at repo info page
* Fix list scroll not smooth
* Change card corner radius from 4dp to 2dp

### Fixes
* Fix crash when repository has no pushed date
